{"tid":1886823,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：ff系列 - 網上搞講座","createTime":"2020-02-19T07:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T07:12:50.000Z","uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c584ada0f6bf8f463a4ef0adf6d02a144a454489","tid":1886823,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"有冇樹木想還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/85238155_547377945868849_579753016534499328_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ohc=MPDAVchpyGsAX9JB9fP&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=357dc51f12a76dacae77a5a08f1315ce&amp;oe=5EC3D7D2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F85238155_547377945868849_579753016534499328_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ohc%3DMPDAVchpyGsAX9JB9fP%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D357dc51f12a76dacae77a5a08f1315ce%26oe%3D5EC3D7D2&h=dcbeaa3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>「風雨季前樹木護養」公眾講座改於網上進行<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  因應新型冠狀病毒疫情的最新情況，發展局今日（二月十九日）宣布，原定於二月二十八日及三月二十五日在香港太空館演講廳，以及三月二十四日在香港中央圖書館演講廳舉辦的「風雨季前樹木護養」公眾講座，將會改以網上視頻形式進行，公衆可在二月二十八日起於發展局綠化、園境及樹木管理組網站（<a href=\"http://www.greening.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greening.gov.hk&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=12a34bb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.greening.gov.hk</a>）觀看。<br />\n   <br />\n  發展局將通知已報名出席的人士。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年2月19日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間11時00分</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.devb.gov.hk/filemanager/tc/content_1008/20170402_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.devb.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_1008%2F20170402_01.jpg&h=c040bcc2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}